Build Requirements
==================

cmake >= 2.8.3

C++11 Compiler:
 * GCC >= 4.6
 * clang >= 3.2
 * ICC >= 13
 * Visual Studio >= 2012

Building and Installing Vc
==========================

* Create a build directory:

$ mkdir build
$ cd build

* Call cmake with the relevant options:

$ cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/opt/Vc -DBUILD_TESTING=OFF <srcdir>

* Build and install:

$ make -j16
$ make install
